WEBVTT - Close Eye Founder Story

scene-0-line-0
00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.530
Hi. I'm Krishna.

scene-0-line-1
00:00:02.580 --> 00:00:03.790
Not the Founder.

scene-0-line-2
00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:04.490
Not the CEO.

scene-0-line-3
00:00:04.540 --> 00:00:05.750
Just Krishna.

scene-1-line-0
00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.510
Thank you for taking a few minutes to listen.

scene-1-line-1
00:00:08.560 --> 00:00:09.970
Before I tell you about Close Eye,

scene-1-line-2
00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:13.250
I want to tell you about one day that changed my life.

scene-2-line-0
00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:15.350
A little while ago, on the 16th of June,

scene-2-line-1
00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:17.310
my daughter was born.

scene-2-line-2
00:00:17.360 --> 00:00:19.450
It was the happiest day of my life.

scene-2-line-3
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:22.290
But somehow, it was also one of the loneliest.

scene-3-line-0
00:00:22.340 --> 00:00:24.950
In that room, there were only a few of us.

scene-3-line-1
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.850
My wife. Our new baby.

scene-3-line-2
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:31.630
My sister-in-law, who stayed with us the whole time.

scene-3-line-3
00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:33.870
And my parents.

scene-3-line-4
00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:36.470
Everyone else I loved was far away.

scene-4-line-0
00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:38.590
There was no crowd outside the door.

scene-4-line-1
00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:40.890
No phone ringing again and again.

scene-4-line-2
00:00:40.940 --> 00:00:43.310
For a few minutes, everything was quiet.

scene-4-line-3
00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:45.350
I held my daughter for the first time.

scene-4-line-4
00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:47.290
I wanted to tell the whole world.

scene-4-line-5
00:00:47.340 --> 00:00:50.790
But I realised — I had almost no one to call.

scene-5-line-0
00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:53.130
Then one thought came to my mind.

scene-5-line-1
00:00:53.180 --> 00:00:55.970
The same thought every parent has:

scene-5-line-2
00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:58.670
“What will happen to her if something happens to me?”

scene-5-line-3
00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:01.270
I didn't want someone to replace her family.

scene-5-line-4
00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:04.330
I wanted something that could make her family stronger.

scene-5-line-5
00:01:04.380 --> 00:01:07.390
Someone she can trust — when we can't be there.

scene-6-line-0
00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:08.890
Then I understood something.

scene-6-line-1
00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:11.330
Millions of families feel this same way.

scene-6-line-2
00:01:11.380 --> 00:01:12.750
Parents getting older.

scene-6-line-3
00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:16.010
Children living far away, in other countries.

scene-6-line-4
00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:18.270
Grandparents missing birthdays.

scene-6-line-5
00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:21.550
Every night, someone is thinking: “Are they okay?”

scene-7-line-0
00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:24.230
That was the moment Close Eye became real for me.

scene-7-line-1
00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:26.150
It was no longer just an idea.

scene-7-line-2
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.510
It became my responsibility.

scene-7-line-3
00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:32.310
So that no family has to face life's big moments alone.

scene-8-line-0
00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:33.870
We don't replace families. We make them stronger.

scene-8-line-1
00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:37.270
We don't replace sons and daughters.

scene-8-line-2
00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:40.650
We help them stay close, even from far away.

scene-8-line-3
00:01:40.700 --> 00:01:42.390
We help families care for each other —

scene-8-line-4
00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:44.950
with love, respect, and trust.

scene-9-line-0
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.050
Every visit. Every message.

scene-9-line-1
00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:48.790
Every companion. Every call.

scene-9-line-2
00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.190
Is a family trusting us.

scene-9-line-3
00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:52.010
When you join Close Eye,

scene-9-line-4
00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:54.210
you are not just joining a company.

scene-9-line-5
00:01:54.260 --> 00:01:57.210
You are becoming someone's trusted presence.

scene-10-line-0
00:01:57.260 --> 00:01:58.190
That day, I made one more promise.

scene-10-line-1
00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:02.370
Close Eye should not grow only for its founders.

scene-10-line-2
00:02:02.420 --> 00:02:04.730
It should grow with the people who build it.

scene-10-line-3
00:02:04.780 --> 00:02:08.230
Work like an owner. Be honest. Protect trust.

scene-10-line-4
00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:11.010
Because trust is not built by software.

scene-10-line-5
00:02:11.060 --> 00:02:12.830
Trust is built by people.

scene-11-line-0
00:02:12.880 --> 00:02:14.610
Every year, on the 16th of June,

scene-11-line-1
00:02:14.660 --> 00:02:15.870
we will celebrate Family Day.

scene-11-line-2
00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:19.330
To remember why Close Eye exists —

scene-11-line-3
00:02:19.380 --> 00:02:21.050
that every request is a real family,

scene-11-line-4
00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:25.630
and that no app can replace a real person being there.

scene-12-line-0
00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:27.270
One day, I hope you will meet my daughter.

scene-12-line-1
00:02:27.320 --> 00:02:28.730
Not because she is our brand.

scene-12-line-2
00:02:28.780 --> 00:02:33.070
But because she reminds us why this work matters.

scene-12-line-3
00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:35.550
Every child deserves grandparents.

scene-12-line-4
00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:39.110
Every grandparent deserves a child's laughter.

scene-12-line-5
00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:41.210
And every family deserves to stay close,

scene-12-line-6
00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:44.150
however far apart they live.

scene-13-line-0
00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:45.610
Please remember one thing.

scene-13-line-1
00:02:45.660 --> 00:02:47.410
Every notification. Every call.

scene-13-line-2
00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:48.930
Every visit. Every decision.

scene-13-line-3
00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:51.910
Is about someone's family.

scene-13-line-4
00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:54.530
Because of your work, someone will sleep peacefully tonight.

scene-13-line-5
00:02:54.580 --> 00:02:56.390
This is our responsibility.

scene-13-line-6
00:02:56.440 --> 00:02:57.890
This is our honour.

scene-13-line-7
00:02:57.940 --> 00:02:59.470
Welcome to Close Eye.

scene-13-line-8
00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:01.590
Thank you for believing in this mission.

scene-13-line-9
00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:03.910
Thank you for becoming part of Close Eye.

scene-13-line-10
00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:06.980
Together, let's build the world's most trusted presence network.
